title: GIVE IT YOUR ALL
itunes:title: GIVE IT YOUR ALL
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
GIVE IT YOUR ALL! Are you tired of being average? Are you giving everything 60%? It's time to make a decision. Enough is Enough. It's time to give it your all and go after your dream. One of the BEST Motivational Speeches of all time featuring Eric Thomas. Music by Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine).

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
